                <div id="outline-container-org4695bff" class="outline-4">
                    <h4 id="org4695bff"><span class="section-number-4">8.1.4</span> multiple-cursors</h4>
                    <div class="outline-text-4" id="text-8-1-4">
                        <p>
                            Configure the shortcuts for multiple cursors.
                        </p>

                        <div class="org-src-container">
