                    </div>

                    <ol class="org-ol">
                        <li><a id="org64536d8"></a>Open remote org dir<br />
                            <div class="outline-text-5" id="text-9-2-1-1">
                                <p>
                                    In your <code>.emacs</code> just add this to configure the location:
                                </p>

