                            Looks convenient <a href="https://github.com/emacsfodder/move-text">here</a>:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="org-ul">
                            <li><code>Meta-up</code> move-text-up (line or active region)</li>
                            <li><code>Meta-down</code> move-text-down (line or active region)</li>
                        </ul>

