                <div id="outline-container-org2d9be04" class="outline-4">
                    <h4 id="org2d9be04"><span class="section-number-4">17.5.5</span> selective display (default: off)</h4>
                    <div class="outline-text-4" id="text-17-5-5">
                        <p>
                            Will fold all text indented more than the position of the cursor at
